classificacao_contabil:
classificacao.mascara ilike
CASE
          WHEN {CATRECEITA_1}::varchar IN ('4') THEN '6211'
          WHEN {CATRECEITA_1}::varchar IN ('9') AND {CARACTERISTICA_PECULIAR}::varchar IN ('105') THEN '6213101'
          WHEN {CATRECEITA_1}::varchar IN ('9') AND {CARACTERISTICA_PECULIAR}::varchar IN ('101') THEN '62132'
          ELSE '62139'
END

classificacao.mascara ilike
CASE
         WHEN {CATRECEITA_1}::varchar IN ('4') THEN '6212'
         ELSE '6211'
END

classificacao.mascara ilike
CASE
         WHEN {CATRECEITA_1}::varchar IN ('4') THEN
                    CASE
                              WHEN {RECURSO_CONTABIL} in (500,501,502) THEN  '72111'
	                      WHEN {RECURSO_CONTABIL} in (860,861,862,869) THEN '72113'
	                      ELSE '72112'
                     END
          ELSE  '8211101'
END

classificacao.mascara ilike
CASE
           WHEN {CATRECEITA_1}::varchar IN ('4') THEN  '8211101'
           ELSE
                     CASE
                              WHEN {CARACTERISTICA_PECULIAR}::varchar IN ('105') THEN '8211404'
                              WHEN {RECURSO_CONTABIL} in (500,501,502) THEN  '72111'
	                      WHEN {RECURSO_CONTABIL} in (860,861,862,869) THEN '72113'
	                      ELSE '72112'
                     END
END
